## How to update the diagram ?

This diagram is generated using [diagrams.net](https://www.diagrams.net/). The `.drawio` file is found in AIT Shared
drive [AIT > HCA Ingest > Documentation > Ingest Service_v2.drawio](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1z4rIWt3O2bVgDtVy0xFSM3a3WGqmMwWE/view?usp=sharing)
To embed, go to `File > Embed > HTML...` create and copy the html and paste in this .md file.

Follow config when creating the html to embed:

* `Links`: Select `Open in New Window`
* `Lightbox` > Select `Edit: Custom` - link to actual `draw.io`` file
